headline: Labcorp to Speak at the 44th Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, announced today that the company will participate in a fireside chat at the 44th Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, Jan. 13, at 4:30 p.m. PT.
